TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select customerId, parent_org_node_code, PARENT_ID, PARENT_NAME, CHILD_CODEID || decode(PARENT_ID, null, null, '~' || PARENT_ID) CHILD_ID, decode(CHILD_org_node_CODE, null, '0', CHILD_org_node_CODE) || decode(PARENT_ID, null, '', '~' || parent_org_node_code) as child_code, CHILD_NAME, CHILD_NODE_ID, category_level from (select node.customer_id as customerId,
node.org_node_id as PARENT_NODEID,
node.org_node_name as PARENT_NAME,
decode(node.org_node_code, null, '0', node.org_node_code || (select (select '~' || org_node_code from org_node, oas.org_node_ancestor ona where org_node.org_node_id = ona.ancestor_org_node_id and ona.number_of_levels = decode(cat.category_level, 4, 1, 3, 1, null) and ona.org_node_id = node.org_node_id) ||
(select '~' || org_node_code from org_node, oas.org_node_ancestor ona where org_node.org_node_id = ona.ancestor_org_node_id and ona.number_of_levels = decode(cat.category_level, 4, 2, null) and ona.org_node_id = node.org_node_id) from dual)
/*node.org_node_code || '~' || node.org_node_name*/) as parent_org_node_code,
decode(node.org_node_code, null, null, node.org_node_code || '~' || node.org_node_name || (select (select '~' || org_node_code || '~' || org_node_name from org_node, oas.org_node_ancestor ona where org_node.org_node_id = ona.ancestor_org_node_id and ona.number_of_levels = decode(cat.category_level, 4, 1, 3, 1, null) and ona.org_node_id = node.org_node_id) ||
(select '~' || org_node_code || '~' || org_node_name from org_node, oas.org_node_ancestor ona where org_node.org_node_id = ona.ancestor_org_node_id and ona.number_of_levels = decode(cat.category_level, 4, 2, null) and ona.org_node_id = node.org_node_id) from dual)
) as parent_id,
child.org_node_id as CHILD_NODE_ID,
child.org_node_name as CHILD_NAME,
decode(decode(cat1.category_level, 4, child.org_node_name, child.org_node_code), null, '0', decode(cat1.category_level, 4, child.org_node_name, child.org_node_code)) || '~' || child.org_node_name as CHILD_CODEID,
decode(cat1.category_level, 4, child.org_node_name, child.org_node_code) as CHILD_org_node_CODE,
cat1.category_level as category_level
from org_node node, org_node child, org_node_category cat, org_node_parent pt, org_node_category cat1 where cat.org_node_category_id = node.org_node_category_id and cat1.org_node_category_id = child.org_node_category_id and child.org_node_id = pt.org_node_id and
node.org_node_id = pt.parent_org_node_id
start with pt.parent_org_node_id = (select org_node_id from oas_stage.stg_param_verify_tb where sno = 1) connect by prior pt.org_node_id = pt.parent_org_node_id order by PARENT_id)

SELECT DISTINCT AB.STUDENT_ID, ORG_NODE_ID, AB.CUSTOMER_ID, AB.RECORD_INDICATOR FROM ORG_NODE, (SELECT STUDENT.STUDENT_ID, STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.CUSTOMER_ID, NVL(LEVEL_1_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_2_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_3_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_4_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_5_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_6_CODE, 0)))))) CODE, NVL(LEVEL_1_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_2_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_3_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_4_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_5_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_6_NAME, 0)))))) NAME, STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.RECORD_INDICATOR AS RECORD_INDICATOR FROM STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL, STUDENT, STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB WHERE STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.PRECODE_ID = STUDENT.PRECODE_ID AND STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID = STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.CUSTOMER_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.PRECODE_ID = STUDENT.PRECODE_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.CUSTOMER_ID = STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.RECORD_INDICATOR IN ($$UPDATE_FLAG,'I')) AB WHERE ORG_NODE.CUSTOMER_ID = AB.CUSTOMER_ID AND ORG_NODE.INFA_LEVEL_CODE = AB.CODE AND ORG_NODE.ORG_NODE_NAME = AB.NAME
union
SELECT DISTINCT STUDENT.STUDENT_ID, STG_EXISTING_ORG_NODE_EXTRACT.CHILD_NODE_ID, STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.CUSTOMER_ID, STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.RECORD_INDICATOR
FROM STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL, STUDENT, ORG_NODE, STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB, STG_EXISTING_ORG_NODE_EXTRACT WHERE STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.PRECODE_ID = STUDENT.PRECODE_ID AND STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID = STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.CUSTOMER_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.PRECODE_ID = STUDENT.PRECODE_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.CUSTOMER_ID = STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.RECORD_INDICATOR IN ('I') AND STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.LEVEL_1_ORG_CODE = STG_EXISTING_ORG_NODE_EXTRACT.CHILD_ORG_NODE_CODE AND ORG_NODE.CUSTOMER_ID = STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID AND not exists (SELECT DISTINCT AB.STUDENT_ID, ORG_NODE_ID, AB.CUSTOMER_ID, AB.RECORD_INDICATOR FROM ORG_NODE, (SELECT STUDENT.STUDENT_ID, STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.CUSTOMER_ID, NVL(LEVEL_1_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_2_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_3_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_4_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_5_CODE, NVL(LEVEL_6_CODE, 0)))))) CODE, NVL(LEVEL_1_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_2_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_3_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_4_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_5_NAME, NVL(LEVEL_6_NAME, 0)))))) NAME, STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.RECORD_INDICATOR AS RECORD_INDICATOR FROM STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL, STUDENT, STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB WHERE STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.PRECODE_ID = STUDENT.PRECODE_ID AND STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID = STG_STUDENT_HIERARCHY_FL.CUSTOMER_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.PRECODE_ID = STUDENT.PRECODE_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.CUSTOMER_ID = STUDENT.CUSTOMER_ID AND STG_STUDENT_BIO_TB.RECORD_INDICATOR IN ($$UPDATE_FLAG,'I')) AB WHERE ORG_NODE.CUSTOMER_ID = AB.CUSTOMER_ID AND ORG_NODE.INFA_LEVEL_CODE = AB.CODE AND ORG_NODE.ORG_NODE_NAME = AB.NAME)
